Schaeuble Wants Greater European Integration, Tagesspiegel Says

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-08-28T10:55:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/schaeuble-wants-greater-european-integration-tagesspiegel-says.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  is calling for greater integration of  Europe ,
 Tagesspiegel  reported, citing an interview.  The euro currency needs a common fiscal policy to be
permanently accepted in financial markets and before euro bonds
can be discussed, the newspaper cited Schaeuble as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story: Ragnhild Kjetland in
Frankfurt at   rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  